text: Pentti Punkari (born 12 January 1938) is a Finnish wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics
